jpeg  
--------------------------------------
A library and utility programs to manipulate jpeg format images

Runtime requirements (these, or newer)
  cygwin-1.5.21-2

Build requirements
  cygwin-1.5.21-2
  gcc-3.4.4
  binutils-20060817-1
  libtool1.5
  autoconf
  autoconf2.5
  automake
  automake1.9

