===========================================================

Build instructions:
  unpack jpeg-6b-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be unpacked
    under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./jpeg-6b-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/jpeg-6b-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/jpeg-6b-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libjpeg-devel-6b-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libjpeg62-6b-X.tar.bz2

Also, 'cygport libpng-1.0.20-X.cygport check' will test the package

===========================================================

To link this library with your projects:
  #1) include jpeglib.h
  #2) to link with the static library, use the '-static' flag 
      when linking
  #3) to link with the dll compile and link as usual; no special flags
      or -Ddefines are necessary

