Port Notes:
----------  jpeg-6b-12 -- 06 Nov 2006 -----------
* Use autotool-ized version from sourceforge
* Split into three, not two, packages
* Use cygport build framework
* Include patches from debian for supporting combined JFIF/EXIF files,
  adding lossless -crop and -perfect options, and new programs for
  manipulating EXIF Orientation tags.  See the man pages for 
    jpegexiforient 
    exifautotran
  or http://sylvana.net/jpegcrop/exif_orientation.html for more info.

There are continue rumblings from the ijg group that 6c will be
coming out "any time now".  Hopefully some of our patches
can get into that release...

